==English==
===Etymology===
[[Category:Greek derivations]]
From [[Ancient Greek]] '''[[χάρμα]]''' (''charma'') "a source of joy, a joy, delight", from '''[[χαίρω]]''' (''chairo'') "to rejoice, to be glad, to be delighted".

